      "span_text": "Current updated guidelines recommend routine administration of PCV13 in series with PPSV23 in all adults 65 years of age or older ( Table 2) .  Based on studies currently available, the combination of PPSV23 with PCV13 should produce a superior immune response than with PPSV23 alone."
